<br /><br />
<br />
<br /><br />
I&#39;ve been staring at the new Shadows stuff for a few days now and this is what came out. I always try to make 1 deck and 5 more spring out of it, so it was hard focusing on what I&#39;d like to do.<br />
<br /><br />
<br />
<br /><br />
Ideally I&#39;d like to make a super Rohandalf deck. Eomer&#39;s always good, Theoden can be around an 11, and the new Gandalf helps out everyone. I know my deck is huge, but I&#39;ve got 3 companions with Muster. Hopefully this will really help move the cards. Muster is also there to trigger my condition removal, Brooding on Tomorrow. Everyone (except Frodo) is mounted so the new move limit +1 card is definately in play for this deck. <br />
<br /><br />
<br />
<br /><br />
As far as the Shadow goes, I&#39;m trying for a little bit of an Uruk swarm. A few of my minions also have Muster, to help move cards. I really don&#39;t know what to say about these guys, I haven&#39;t seen them in action yet.<br />
<br /><br />
<br />
<br /><br />
Well, let me know what you think.  </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
